title: I just got matched against a 5 man pre made in a full team of solo queuers.
body: Seriously? Dynamic Queue is working out great Riot....

replies.body: You should email support because that's definitely not intended. Riot will actually look up the game in question to check if matchmaking did indeed mess up.
Evidence? Or just QQ because lost
How do I provide evidence for that?

What made you think it was a 5 man team? I assume it was your Graham's game that matches the time of this post ... In which case the fact that 3 of them have Chinese names makes me very much doubt it was a group of 5. 

I conclude QQ
Graham? Gragas? No it was the fact that they all had the same club name it was like 8IIIIID or however many I's there were
You are lying. The plebs crying for Solo Q are getting ridiculous.
Its happened to me before. It probably will happen again.
